    {
      "id": "chat-col-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 95,
      "y": 210,
      "width": 350,
      "height": 230,
      "text": "Session Bar\n  [Voice toggle] [Panel toggle] [End Session]\n\nMessageBlock + PartRenderer\n  Text → Markdown + ruby/furigana\n  Panel tools → ReferencePill (when panel open)\n  Inline tools → ChoiceButtons\n  Difficulty badges [食べる N2]\n\nSuggestionChips (from suggestActions)\nEscapeHatch\n\nChatInput\n  Japanese IME (useJapaneseIME)\n  VoiceControls (useVoice → STT)\n  IME toggle, Romaji toggle",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
