    {
      "id": "routes-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 95,
      "y": 912,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 190,
      "text": "/conversation/plan        POST\n  → Haiku generates SessionPlan\n/conversation/plan/update  POST (NEW)\n  → User edits plan from panel\n/conversation/send         POST (SSE)\n  → Re-reads plan from DB each turn\n  → Appends plan to system prompt\n/conversation/end          POST\n/conversation/xray         POST\n/voice/stt                 POST (NEW)\n  → gpt-4o-mini-transcribe\n/tts                       POST\n  → voice + speed params (NEW)\n/profile                   GET PATCH",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
